3.0 The Pipe

The Native Pipe is better because its minimalist, its available all time (since its native) and also allowed te base R to jettison infrequently used features.

4.0 Groups

flights |> 
  group_by(month) |> 
  summarize(
    avg_delay = mean(dep_delay, na.rm=TRUE),
    count_delay = n()
  )

flights |> 
  group_by(dest) |> 
  slice_max(arr_delay, n = 2, with_ties = FALSE) |> 
  relocate(dest, arr_delay)

daily <- flights |> 
  group_by(year, month, day)

daily

  summarize( n = n(), .groups="keep") |> 
  ungroup()

  summarize(
    delay = mean(dep_delay, na.rm=TRUE),
    n = n(),
    .by = c(year, month)
  )
